[Inflating ens spread and vertical localization w.r.t. pblh obs location]
------------------------------------------

-----PROCEDURE-----
! For inflating ens spread and modifying hybrid vertical localization length scale near PBLH obs,
! 1) Save pblh obs grid information (global domain in ens grid) in obs_para.f90
! 2) inflate ens spread near PBLH obs
! 3) Modify hybrid vertical localization length scale near PBLH obs in init_rf_z in hybrid_ensemble_isotropic.f90

! 1) Save pblh obs grid information (global domain in ens grid) <- disobs in obs_para.f90 
!    - 1a) inflatation coefficient for t and q
!          -> ges_coef_inf_ens_grid_global(ix:ixp,iy:iyp,iz,it:itp)=coef (+- 2 levels? with Gaussian dis)
!    - 1b) vertical localization
!          -> ges_vlocal_ens_grid_global(ix:ixp,iy:iyp,iz,1)=1.0
!      >>> hybrid_ensemble_parameters.f90
!      >>> hybrid_ensemble_isotropic.f90 (subroutine create_ensemble: allocate)
!      >>> obs_para.f90 (subroutine disobs in obs_para.f90)
! 2) Multiply ens perturbation by inflation coeff 
!      >>> get_gefs_ensperts_dualres (it is called in load_ensemble)
! 4) Modify hybrid vertical localization length scale near PBLH obs
!      >>> hybrid_ensemble_isotropic.f90 (subroutine init_rf_z in hybrid_ensemble_isotropic.f90)

-----CODE-----
! 0) (Declare) hybrid_ensemble_parameters.f90
! 1) subroutine disobs in obs_para.f90
     - assignment of pblhobs to modify ens spread and vertical localization 
       obs_para is called at the end of observer_set (after read_obs)
! 2) get_gefs_ensperts_dualres.f90
! 3) init_rf_z in hybrid_ensemble_isotropic.f90


